commit.message:
re PR testsuite/86745 (gcc.target/i386/avx-cvt-2.c etc. FAIL on 64-bit x86)

	PR testsuite/86745
	* gcc.target/i386/avx-cvt-2.c: Loosen scan-assembler strings.
	* gcc.target/i386/avx-cvt-2.c: Ditto.

From-SVN: r263598

files.patch:
